<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Image Quality Testing Grid</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 2em; }
        .quality-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 1em 0;
        }
        .quality-cell {
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .fine-lines {
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #000,
                #000 1px,
                #fff 1px,
                #fff 2px
            );
        }
        .diagonal-lines {
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                45deg,
                #000,
                #000 1px,
                #fff 1px,
                #fff 2px
            );
        }
        .small-text { font-size: 6px; line-height: 1.2; }
        .gradient { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #000, #fff); color: #666; }
        .circles {
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #000 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 5px 5px;
        }
        .color-bars {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet);
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px black;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Image Quality Testing Grid</h1>

    <p>This grid contains various patterns to test image quality, sharpness, and detail preservation:</p>

    <div class="quality-grid">
        <div class="quality-cell fine-lines">Fine Vertical Lines</div>
        <div class="quality-cell diagonal-lines">Diagonal Lines</div>
        <div class="quality-cell gradient">Gradient</div>
        <div class="quality-cell circles">Dot Pattern</div>

        <div class="quality-cell small-text">
            Small Text
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor.
        </div>
        <div class="quality-cell" style="background: #f0f0f0; border: 2px solid #999;">
            Border
            Detail
        </div>
        <div class="quality-cell color-bars">Color Spectrum</div>
        <div class="quality-cell" style="background: repeating-conic-gradient(from 0deg, #000 0deg 45deg, #fff 45deg 90deg);">
            Radial
            Pattern
        </div>

        <div class="quality-cell" style="font-family: serif; font-size: 8px;">
            Serif Font
            The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.
        </div>
        <div class="quality-cell" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 8px;">
            Monospace
            1234567890
            abcdefghijk
        </div>
        <div class="quality-cell" style="background: #000; color: #fff;">
            High
            Contrast
            White on Black
        </div>
        <div class="quality-cell" style="background: #ddd; color: #999;">
            Low
            Contrast
            Gray on Gray
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Testing Notes</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Check fine line rendering and aliasing</li>
        <li>Verify text clarity at small sizes</li>
        <li>Test gradient smoothness</li>
        <li>Examine color reproduction accuracy</li>
        <li>Assess detail preservation in patterns</li>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>